title: Vanessa Bayer can sell anything!
description: Hilarious Actress, Comedian and Home Shopping Network aficionado Vanessa Bayer is back on Bitch Sesh to talk about She by Herself, Diana's hotel rituals and how Kyle's dogs are ruining her house! Plus, she asks the most important question about Dubai which is... "Do we have a show?" The answer is still unclear but what is clear is that Lisa Rinna needs to watch her back because there is a new QVC head bitch in town and her name is Vanessa Bayer.
